khola hawa is a 2014 bengali film directed by anup das and produced by white mist productions .   the film is a strong insight into psychological dilemma about the meaning of life and happiness , a story between a middle age housewife and a young guy .   the film stars rituparna sengupta and samadarshi dutta in the lead roles , with lalita chatterjee , saswati guha thakurata , pradip chakraborty , ekavali khanna , bidita bag & joy sengupta in supporting roles .   khola hawa released on 12 december 2014 .